                            <comment id="12993291" author="haploid" created="Fri, 11 Feb 2011 01:21:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As a followup comment to this issue, I found a workaround.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if you add any Form at all to the &lt;b&gt;target&lt;/b&gt; page, wicket will function correctly.  By adding the following to my Base WebPage, the issue goes away completely:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;add( new Form( &quot;kludgyhack&quot; ) );&lt;/p&gt;
